Title: Coconut Musk
Description: Coconut Musk smells creamy, soft, and tropical — combining the milky sweetness of coconut with the clean, powdery warmth of musk. It’s smooth, comforting, and sun-kissed, with a gentle, skin-like finish that feels effortlessly relaxing.

Title: Pure Musk
Description: Pure Musk smells like crisp linen and gentle powder — bright, fresh, and softly clean. It has a subtle, soothing warmth with a silky, delicate finish that feels refreshing, light, and naturally elegant.

Title: Rose Musk
Description: Rose Musk smells elegant, romantic, and airy — a blend of fresh, dewy roses and soft, powdery musk. It’s floral yet clean, with a delicate sweetness and a smooth, lingering trail that feels timeless and graceful.

Title: Vanilla Musk
Description: Vanilla Musk smells warm, soft, and inviting — combining the sweet, creamy richness of vanilla with the clean, powdery smoothness of musk. It’s cozy, slightly sensual, and beautifully balanced for everyday wear.

Title: Sandal Musk
Description: Sandal Musk smells soft, creamy, and comforting — blending the warm, smooth woodiness of sandalwood with the clean, powdery elegance of musk. It’s gentle, skin-like, and subtly sensual with a serene warmth.

Title: Silver Dust
Description: Silver Dust smells sweet, smooth, and modern — opening with juicy berries and soft florals, grounded by creamy musk, amber, and a hint of sweetness. Clean, modern, and subtly addictive.

Title: Shay Oud
Description: Shay Oud is a rich, luxurious fragrance made from oud (agarwood). It smells warm, woody, slightly sweet, and smoky — with hints of spice and leather. Bold, deep, and elegant.

Title: Musk Al Qurashi
Description: Musk Al Qurashi smells soft, clean, and elegant — a blend of powdery white musk with gentle floral and amber notes. It's fresh, slightly sweet, and effortlessly refined.

Title: Fawakeh
Description: Fawakeh smells bright, juicy, and sweet — a vibrant mix of fresh, ripe fruits with a tropical twist.

Title: Rouat Al Oud by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Rouat Al Oud by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance of elegance and mystery, made for those who wish to leave a lasting impression. It opens with the golden warmth of saffron blended with the sweet juiciness of raspberry, a contrast that immediately intrigues. At its heart blooms a lush bouquet of rose and geranium, deepened by earthy patchouli, adding richness and sophistication. The journey settles into a powerful base where smoky agarwood and smooth leather meet glowing amber and cedar, creating a trail that is both commanding and refined. Sensual yet dignified, Rouat Al Oud is a fragrance that speaks of strength, luxury, and timeless allure—perfect for evenings, special occasions, or whenever you want to feel truly unforgettable.

Top Notes: Saffron and Raspberry.

Middle Notes: Rose, Geranium and Patchouli.

Base Notes: Agarwood (Oud), Amber, Leather and Cedar.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Ser Al Khulood by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Ser Al Khulood by Lattafa is a fragrance that feels like a fairytale written in soft, golden ink. It opens with the luscious sweetness of ripe strawberries, sprinkled with delicate sugar crystals, evoking the charm of an enchanted orchard at twilight. As the heart unfolds, tuberose and jasmine bloom like moonlit flowers, their petals whispering secrets of elegance and mystery. The journey ends with a warm embrace of vanilla, amber, and musk, wrapping the senses in a velvety glow, like a starlit night woven with dreams. Both playful and sensual, this perfume is a tale of sweetness and depth, perfect for those who wish to leave behind a trail of magic wherever they go.

Top Notes: Big Strawberry and Sugar.

Middle Notes: Tuberose and Jasmine.

Base Notes: Vanilla, Amber and Musk.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Sa'ud by Asdaaf (Lattafa Perfumes)
Description:
Sa’ud by Asdaaf is like a tale whispered under moonlight — a fragrance where elegance meets mystery. It begins with a sparkling burst of mandarin orange, bergamot, and sun-kissed orange, like the first light breaking through enchanted skies. The heart unfurls into a delicate garden of jasmine and rose, their petals weaving a soft, romantic spell. As the story deepens, the base reveals a velvety embrace of warm woods, silky musk, and the mystical richness of oud, wrapped once more in jasmine’s gentle caress. Both luminous and profound, Sa’ud is a scent that feels timeless — a journey through hidden gardens and starlit nights, perfect for dreamers who crave both light and depth in their fragrance.

Top Notes: Mandarin Orange, Bergamot and Orange.

Middle Notes: Jasmine and Rose.

Base Notes: Woody Notes, Musk, Oud and Jasmine.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Breeze by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Breeze by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that captures the essence of air flowing through sunlit horizons. It opens with the sparkling brightness of bergamot, gently lifted by spicy cardamom and a veil of incense, evoking the feeling of a fresh dawn. The heart reveals a delicate blend of jasmine and cyclamen, soft florals that bloom like petals carried by the wind. As the fragrance settles, warm cedar, smooth sandalwood, and velvety musk create a serene, comforting base that lingers gracefully on the skin. Both invigorating and soothing, Breeze is a scent of freedom and calm — perfect for those who wish to carry a touch of freshness and elegance wherever they go.

Top Notes: Bergamot, Incense and Cardamom.

Middle Notes: Jasmine and Cyclamen.

Base Notes: Musk, Cedar and Sandalwood.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Raw Human by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Raw Human by Lattafa Perfumes is a daring fragrance that captures the essence of contrasts—soft fruit, tender florals, and rugged depth. It opens with a burst of ripe apricot and dark plum, brightened by a hint of pink pepper that adds a playful spark. At its heart lies the refined note of osmanthus, lending a velvety floral sweetness touched with subtle apricot nuances. Title: Bade'e Al Oud Noble Blush by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Bade’e Al Oud Noble Blush by Lattafa Perfumes is a delicate dream bottled into scent. It opens with the tender sweetness of rose milk, soft and creamy like a whisper of romance. At the heart, a gourmand swirl of meringue and almond adds playful elegance, evoking the charm of a Parisian patisserie. The fragrance then melts into a comforting base of vanilla, musk, and smooth sandalwood, leaving behind a warm, velvety embrace that lingers on the skin. Both graceful and addictive, Noble Blush is perfect for those who crave a fragrance that is at once feminine, deliciously sweet, and luxuriously soft—a scent that feels like a gentle blush of love and light.

Top Note: Rose Milk.

Middle Notes: Meringue and Almond.

Base Notes: Vanilla, Musk and Sandalwood.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Eclaire by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Eclaire by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that feels like stepping into a golden, dreamlike patisserie. It opens with the irresistible sweetness of caramel, milk, and sugar, melting together like a delicate dessert. As it unfolds, golden honey drizzles over soft white flowers, adding both warmth and elegance. Finally, the base reveals a comforting embrace of vanilla, praline, and velvety musk, leaving behind a trail that is both indulgent and graceful.

Top Notes: Caramel, Milk and Sugar.

Middle Notes: Honey and White Flowers.

Base Notes: Vanilla, Praline and Musk.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Haya by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Haya by Lattafa Perfumes is a sparkling celebration of elegance and joy. It opens with a dazzling burst of champagne bubbles blended with the sweetness of strawberry, the brightness of tangerine, and the richness of blood orange, kissed softly by rose. As the fragrance unfolds, a bouquet of gardenia and jasmine blooms with the exotic charm of vanilla orchid, creating a romantic and feminine heart. Finally, the scent settles into a warm and comforting base of amber, creamy sandalwood, and toasted chestnut, leaving a trail that feels both luxurious and inviting. Radiant, playful, yet deeply sophisticated, Haya is a fragrance for the woman who shines effortlessly and captivates every room she enters.

Top Notes: Champagne, Strawberry, Tangerine, Blood Orange and Rose.

Middle Notes: Gardenia, Jasmine and Vanilla Orchid.

Base Notes: Amber, Sandalwood and Chestnut.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Ana Abiyedh by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Ana Abiyedh by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that whispers elegance in its purest form. It opens with a fresh and luminous touch of bergamot and orange, evoking the brightness of a golden sunrise. As the heart unfolds, delicate pear and soft vanilla create a sweet and creamy harmony, adding a gentle warmth that feels both inviting and refined. The base lingers with sensual musk and glowing amber, wrapping the fragrance in a veil of sophistication and comfort. Minimalistic yet captivating, Ana Abiyedh is a scent for those who embrace subtle beauty and timeless grace, leaving behind an effortlessly unforgettable trail.

Top Notes: Bergamot and Orange.

Middle Notes: Vanilla and Pear.

Base Notes: Musk and Amber.

We have it available in the original sealed 60 ml EDP package.

Title: Ana Abiyedh Poudrée by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Ana Abiyedh Poudrée by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that feels like soft silk brushing against the skin. It opens with a delicate bouquet of orange blossom, jasmine, and rose, painting a picture of elegance and purity. At its heart lies the tender embrace of musk, smooth and powdery, creating an intimate aura that lingers close. As it settles, the base reveals a warm and sophisticated blend of vanilla and tonka bean, gently balanced with cedar, patchouli, and vetiver, adding depth and refinement. The result is a fragrance that is both airy and sensual, perfect for those who want to leave a trail of soft allure wherever they go. A scent of grace, confidence, and timeless femininity.

Top Notes: Orange Blossom, Jasmine and Rose.

Middle Note: Musk.

Base Notes: Vanilla, Tonka Bean, Cedar, Patchouli and Vetiver.

We have it available in the original sealed 60 ml EDP package.

Title: Afeef by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Afeef by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that opens like the first rays of dawn—bright, soft, and full of promise. Juicy peach and sparkling bergamot mingle with a playful hint of pink pepper, creating a lively and elegant introduction. The heart blooms into a bouquet of white florals—tuberose, jasmine, and orange blossom—that feels both luminous and graceful, wrapping you in a radiant aura. As the scent settles, a warm and sensual base emerges, with praline’s delicate sweetness melting into creamy sandalwood, golden amber, and earthy patchouli. The result is a perfume that feels modern yet timeless, sweet yet sophisticated—perfect for those who want their presence to linger like a beautiful memory. Afeef is not just a fragrance, but an enchanting signature of charm and confidence.

Top Notes: Peach, Pink Pepper and Bergamot.

Middle Notes: Tuberose, Jasmine and Orange Blossom.

Base Notes: Praline, Sandalwood, Amber and Patchouli.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: The Kingdom (Men) by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
The Kingdom by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that feels both regal and magnetic, created for the man who carries himself with quiet strength and elegance. It opens with a refreshing blend of lavender, mint, and sage — crisp and invigorating like the first breath of dawn. Soon, warmth unfolds as creamy vanilla and rich tobacco weave with the subtle sweetness of orange blossom, striking a balance between refinement and allure. In its depth, tonka, benzoin, and labdanum create a smoky-amber embrace, leaving behind a trail that is both powerful and comforting. Bold yet sophisticated, this scent captures the essence of timeless masculinity — a fragrance that lingers long after you’ve left the room, commanding attention without saying a word. A true statement of strength, mystery, and charm.

Top Notes: Lavender, Mint and Sage.

Middle Notes: Vanilla, Tobacco and Orange Blossom.

Base Notes: Tonka, Benzoin and Labdanum.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Khamrah Qahwa by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Khamrah Qahwa by Lattafa is an enchanting fragrance that feels like a warm embrace on a star-lit night. It opens with a golden swirl of cinnamon, cardamom, and ginger—spices that awaken the senses with their exotic fire. As the journey unfolds, the heart reveals a gourmand treasure: praline sweetness wrapped in candied fruits, softened by delicate white flowers that whisper elegance. The base is a rich, addictive blend where velvety vanilla and roasted coffee meet the creamy depth of tonka bean, glowing benzoin, and sensual musk. Together, they create a trail that is both comforting and irresistibly magnetic. Khamrah Qahwa is more than a perfume—it’s a story of warmth, indulgence, and luxury, perfect for those who want to leave behind a lasting impression of sweet sophistication.

Top Notes: Cinnamon, Cardamom and Ginger.

Middle Notes: Praline, Candied Fruits and White Flowers.

Base Notes: Vanilla, Coffee, Tonka Bean, Benzoin and Musk.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Fakhar Rose by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Fakhar Rose by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that feels like stepping into an enchanted garden at dawn. The first breath greets you with sparkling fruits, delicate lily, and the juicy allure of pomegranate, kissed by airy aldehydes for a radiant opening. As the scent unfolds, a bouquet of white florals, tuberose, jasmine, gardenia, and ylang-ylang, blends with the soft sweetness of honeysuckle, rose, and peony, creating a heart that is both romantic and luminous. Finally, the base wraps you in a velvety cocoon of creamy vanilla, tender white musk, smooth sandalwood, and the modern glow of ambroxan. Feminine yet powerful, this perfume captures elegance and joy in every drop, making it perfect for women who love to leave a graceful, unforgettable trail.

Top Notes: Fruits, Lily, Pomegranate and Aldehydes.

Middle Notes: Tuberose, Jasmine, Gardenia, Ylang-Ylang, Honeysuckle, Rose and Peony.

Base Notes: Vanilla, White Musk, Sandalwood and Ambroxan.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Sehr by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Sehr by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance woven from contrasts, rich and magnetic like a secret spell. It begins with the sharp allure of bitter almond softened by the fiery warmth of cinnamon, a daring invitation that sparks curiosity. At its heart, Akigalawood’s mysterious spiciness entwines with the fruity sweetness of Pomarose and the delicate glow of jasmine, creating a captivating aura both modern and timeless. As the scent settles, it unveils a sensual base of creamy vanilla absolute, velvety tonka bean, and golden amber, wrapping the skin in a trail of elegance and comfort. Bold yet refined, Sehr is a fragrance for those who embrace intensity and charm, leaving behind an unforgettable presence.

Top Notes: Bitter Almond and Cinnamon.

Middle Notes: Akigalawood, Pomarose and Jasmine.

Base Notes: Vanilla Absolute, Tonka Bean and Amber.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Maahir Black by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Maahir Black by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance woven from contrasts - bold, smoky, and irresistibly magnetic. It opens with the fiery sparkle of black and pink pepper, softened by the golden warmth of saffron, setting the stage for a daring olfactory journey. The heart unfolds into a mysterious blend of cade oil and labdanum, touched with the resinous depth of gurjan balsam and the unexpected tartness of rhubarb, creating intrigue and intensity. As the scent settles, it reveals a commanding base of leather and cedar, enriched with guaiac wood, patchouli, moss, and musk, leaving behind a trail that is both rugged and refined. Maahir Black is not just a perfume - it’s a statement of power, elegance, and untamed allure, crafted for those who dare to stand apart.

Top Notes: Black Pepper, Pink Pepper and Saffron.

Middle Notes: Cade Oil, Labdanum, Gurjan Balsam and Rhubarb.

Base Notes: Leather, Cedar, Guaiac Wood, Patchouli, Moss and Musk.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Maahir Legacy by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Maahir Legacy by Lattafa Perfumes is a fragrance that speaks of timeless strength and magnetic charm. It opens with a dazzling burst of lime, mint, grapefruit, lavender, and juicy pineapple, evoking freshness as bright as a sunrise on a new horizon. The heart unfolds with a bold interplay of black pepper, juniper berry, rosemary, geranium, and smoky frankincense — an aromatic balance between fiery spice and deep mystique. Finally, the base lingers with the powerful warmth of ambroxan, earthy vetiver, oakmoss, and cashmeran, softened by the subtle sweetness of tonka bean. The result is a fragrance that is fresh yet grounded, modern yet classic, a true legacy in scent. Perfect for the man who wishes to leave an unforgettable impression wherever he goes.

Top Notes: Lime, Mint, Grapefruit, Lavender and Pineapple.

Middle Notes: Black Pepper, Juniper Berry, Rosemary, Geranium and Frankincense.

Base Notes: Ambroxan, Vetiver, Oakmoss, Cashmeran and Tonka Bean.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.

Title: Yara Tous by Lattafa Perfumes
Description:
Yara Tous by Lattafa Perfumes is a dreamy escape bottled into fragrance. It opens with a lush burst of tropical mango, creamy coconut, and juicy passionfruit, painting a picture of golden sunsets and carefree laughter. The heart blooms with delicate jasmine and luminous orange blossom, softened by the powdery sweetness of heliotrope, adding a touch of elegance to its playful soul. As the scent settles, comforting vanilla melts into velvety musk and smooth cashmeran, leaving a lingering trail that feels both warm and enchanting. Yara Tous is a fragrance that balances tropical vibrance with soft sophistication, perfect for those who want to carry a touch of paradise with them wherever they go.

Top Notes: Mango, Coconut and Passionfruit.

Middle Notes: Jasmine, Orange Blossom and Heliotrope.

Base Notes: Vanilla, Musk and Cashmeran.

We have it available in the original sealed 100 ml EDP package.
